<p>
<a href="./NerdanelVampire">NerdanelVampire</a>: The shows look interesting. I think Brimstone was on air here at one time but I missed it. Perhaps it'll get aired again before 2020. Public domain material is much nicer in this respect. The <a href="./Clark_20Ashton_20Smith">Clark Ashton Smith</a> page has links to sites that host his stories on the Internet. I like the Zothique stories in particular. I think they have the potential to make a game with a nice and different atmosphere. 
</p>
